title: Seeking Caretaker/Caretaker team-Uptown/Lakes
posting_body: ['Hornig Companies is seeking dedicated and enthusiastic individuals or a team to help manage the upkeep and day-to-day functions of its 3033 James Ave.', 'S.  location in the Uptown/Lakes area of Minneapolis.', ' We are seeking clean, detail oriented, caring persons and, typically, living on-site is necessary.', ' This is a part-time commitment and hours are somewhat flexible.', ' Compensation is in the form of a rent credit of  $300 a month for caretaking with an additional $15/hour paid for cleaning turnover apartments.', '  Photos are not from this apartment but are from a similar apartment in the building.', 'Caretaking responsibilities include, but are not limited to, showing and leasing apartments, maintaining cleanliness of common areas, apartment turnover cleaning, seasonal grounds keeping (watering shrubs, weeding, shoveling sidewalks in winter, ice control) and being "eyes and ears" of the property.', '3033 James Ave.', "S. is a well-maintained 1960's 14 unit building in the Uptown/Lakes area of Minneapolis.", '   The caretaker apartment  is a 500 square foot garden level 1BR apartment with wood-look vinyl floors renting at $930 per month with heat, cooking gas and trash removal included and residents paying electricity, water/sewer and cable/internet.', ' This  no smoking building.', 'Up to 2 cats are allowed with additional deposit and monthly fees.', ' Off-street parking available for an additional fee.', 'Fair Housing, leasing and caretaking training will be provided.', ' Property caretaking, custodial or customer service experience is preferred.', ' Please email your resume  including a brief statement as to why this position is for you and any other information you feel may be beneficial.']
